<br>
While this is a game that we play, there are real people who sit behind those screens.  Real feelings, real emotions, real situations.  I challenge each of you to try and make a difference in this recent tragedy we have witnissed in the last day.  I have given blood and donated what little money I had for lunch to the American Red Cross.  Someone in our guild has been actived on her reserve unit and running a burn triage transport in NY city last I heard, leaving her family behind to go help those in need.  <br>
<br>
Let us make a difference in helping those who need it during this time.  We are a community of different individuals, but all share the same feelings for the most part in regards to this.<br>
<br>
I have started a thread on our message boards, and you are welcome to post there.  <br>
